## 🛠️ Recommended Chrome Extensions
To use this workflow, you need one of these "Scraper" extensions:
1. **Instant Data Scraper** (Free/Easy): Automatically detects lists on any web page including Maps.
2. **Outscraper Google Maps Extension**: Specialized for maps; more accurate but might have limits.
3. **Web Scraper (webscraper.io)**: More advanced; requires setting up a "Sitemap".

---

## 🚀 Why use this instead of the API?

| Feature | Chrome Extension Method | Direct API Method (Current) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Cost** | **FREE** (mostly) | Requires API credits |
| **Speed** | Manual (1-2 mins per batch) | Instant (seconds) |
| **Quality** | High (You verify visually) | Raw (Requires filtering) |
| **Scaling** | Harder to automate fully | Perfectly automated |

